10 A. Yes

14 A. IMDB?

16 A. Yes
17 Q. And if those were listed in your IMDB, would those indicate
18 that you were involved with those productions?
19 MS. POMERANTZ: Objection, your Honor.
20 THE COURT: Grounds?

22 THE COURT: Sustained.
23 Q. Do you look at your listings to see whether they are
24 accurate or not?
25 A. No
